Replace the body of `DrainAsync` (lines 105–260) with the loop-based version below. The existing variable declarations (`results`, `circuitBreaker`, `_pauseRequested`, `drainCts`, `drainRunId`, `configResult`, `skipPlanning`) remain unchanged; the snapshot line 115 is replaced and the Phase-1 and Phase-2 blocks are wrapped in a `while (true)` loop with a `firstPass` guard.

