4. **Phase 2** — Add `seenIds.Add(task.Id)` immediately after `queue.RemoveAt(0)` / before execution (line 208 area).

5. **Sequential-only new-task check** — After the lifecycle/summary-log block for a completed task and before the circuit-breaker check, insert:
   ```csharp
   if (skipPlanning)
   {
       var newTasks = CollectNewTasks(Tasks, seenIds);
       if (newTasks.Count > 0)
       {
           foreach (var nt in newTasks) seenIds.Add(nt.Id);
